    "Even outside of the humanities, keeping up with students was a significant motivating factor for instructors to begin incorporating generative AI into their teaching activities.",
    "Learning Objectives and AI Literacy",
    "Much of the conversation around integrating generative AI into student learning came back to learning objectives.",
    "Instructors are asking themselves: what is most important for my students to learn?",
    "Can generative AI be leveraged to serve my learning objectives?"
